        <h2 id="info-title">How We Use Collected Information</h2>
        <div class="info-content">
            <div class="info-text">
                <p>
                    Girls Who Connect collects and stores certain information to enable core features
                    and personalise your experience. This includes:
                </p>

                <ul>
                    <li>Username - used to identify you within the app and display on your profile</li>
