    <div class="info-inner">
        <h2 id="info-title">How Advertisements Use Information</h2>
        <div class="info-content">
            <div class="info-text">
                <p>
                    Information collected by third-party services such as Google AdMob may be used for:
                </p>

                <ul>
                    <li>Serving personalised advertisements relevant to your interests and behaviour</li>
                    <li>Measuring the effectiveness of adverts displayed in the app</li>
                    <li>Providing aggregated reporting to help us understand user engagement with ads</li>
                    <li>Improving ad quality, frequency, and relevance based on user data</li>
                </ul>

                <p>
                    For more details on how Google uses this data, you may review Google's advertising
                    privacy policies directly.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-inner">
        <h2 id="info-title">Optional Image Review for Support</h2>
        <div class="info-content">
            <div class="info-text">
                <p>
                    If there is an issue with scanning or processing a receipt, Bill E may give you the
                    option to send the receipt image to us for further review and support.
                </p>

                <p>
                    This will only happen if you explicitly choose to allow it. Your receipt image will
                    not be sent for manual review automatically.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Any images you choose to share in this way will only be used to investigate the issue,
                    improve the accuracy of the app, and provide support where needed.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-inner">
        <h2 id="info-title">Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <div class="info-content">
            <div class="info-text">
                <p>
                    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected
                    with a new effective date listed at the top of this page.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-inner">
        <h2 id="info-title">Contact</h2>
        <div class="info-content">
            <div class="info-text">
                <p>
                    If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
                    matt@kenyondevlabs.com.
                </p>

                <p>
                    By using Bill E, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to
                    the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. If you have any questions, suggestions, or
                    concerns, you can send feedback or report issues directly within the app using the
                    built-in feedback and reporting features.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* ===== Info Section (Text + Image) ===== */
    .info-section {
        color: #111;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        background: #fff;
        margin-top: -20px;
    }

    .info-inner {
        width: min(var(--page-max, 1100px), 100%);
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .info-section h2 {
        text-align: left;
        font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        margin: 1rem 0 0.75rem 0;
    }

    .info-content {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 2rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .info-text {
        flex: 1 1 480px;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        min-width: 0;
        text-align: left;
    }

        .info-text p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

    .info-image {
        flex: 1 1 420px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        min-width: 0;
    }

        .info-image img {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: var(--radius, 16px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
        }

    /* ===== Responsive Stack ===== */
    @@media (max-width: 800px) {
        .info-content {
            flex-direction: column-reverse;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            text-align: left;
            gap: 0rem;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .info-text,
        .info-image {
            flex: 0 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
        }

            .info-image img {
                max-width: 360px;
            }

        .info-section h2 {
            text-align: left;
        }
    }
</style>

<hr class="section-divider" />
<!-- ===== Site Footer ===== -->
<footer class="site-footer" aria-labelledby="footer-title">
    <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-grid">

            <!-- Legal -->
            <nav class="footer-block" aria-label="Legal">
                <h3>Legal</h3>
                <ul class="footer-list">
                    <li><NavLink href="/GirlsWhoConnect/PrivacyPolicy">Privacy Policy</NavLink></li>
                    <li><NavLink href="/GirlsWhoConnect/ChildSafetyStandards">Child Safety Standards</NavLink></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>

        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .site-footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        color: #111;
        text-align: center; /* Center everything */
    }

        .site-footer .footer-inner {
            width: min(var(--page-max, 900px), 100%); /* ✅ prevent overflow in parent */
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1rem 2.5rem; /* ✅ small gutters on mobile */
            box-sizing: border-box; /* ✅ sizing safety */
        }

    /* Stack vertically instead of grid */
    .footer-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-block {
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 100%; /* ✅ let it center and shrink gracefully */
    }

        .footer-block h3 {
            margin: 0 0 .5rem 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .footer-block p,
        .footer-address,
        .footer-list,
        .footer-actions,
        .footer-bottom {
            margin: 0.25rem 0;
            color: #333;
        }

    .footer-address {
        font-style: normal;
    }

    .footer-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0.25rem 0;
        display: flex;
        gap: .75rem 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center; /* center them */
    }

        .footer-list li {
            margin: .35rem 0;
        }

        .footer-list a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #111;
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
        }

            .footer-list a:hover {
                color: var(--brand, #6a54e8);
                border-bottom-color: currentColor;
            }

    /* Buttons */
    .footer-actions {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: .75rem;
        margin: .5rem 0;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 520px; /* ✅ nice width on small screens */
    }

    .btn-footer {
        padding: .5rem .9rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        background: none;
        border: 1px solid #6a54e8;
        color: #111;
        transition: color .12s ease, border-color .12s ease;
    }

        .btn-footer:hover {
            color: var(--brand, #6a54e8);
            border-color: var(--brand, #6a54e8);
        }

        .btn-footer.ghost {
            opacity: 0.75;
        }

            .btn-footer.ghost:hover {
                opacity: 1;
            }

    .footer-bottom {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: .9rem;
        color: #444;
    }

    /* Divider between sections */
    hr.section-divider {
        border: none;
        height: 4px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 10px auto;
        background: #6a54e8;
        border-radius: 0;
        padding-inline: 10px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
</style>